A '''dual-drive system''' was a combination of an [[intra-system]] and [[intra-galactic engine]], or drive, setup. Intra-system drives included anti-grav and [[Ion engine/Legends|ion engines]]. [[Hyperdrive/Legends|Hyperdrives]] constituted the other part of the dual-drive system. They could only be activated once out of a planet's gravity well, but they enable paralight travel.

